race.description: Prost @ Aquis Stallions Mm Country Cup Qualifier Hcp
race.comment: PARTY SPIRIT (6) has been improving with racing this time in work and that culminated with a dominant Ipswich victory last time out. Will have derived some confidence from that win and can go right on with the job now. TAKE A BOW (9) has only missed a drum once in six starts over this sprint journey and is drawn to get a gun run in transit from the inside alley. Capable of a big perofrmance. Former NSW galloper ARCTIC LEGEND (7) resumes here for the new stable but the form he showed down south was good enough for a race of this calibre. Respect any push in betting. OBEROI PRINCESS (5) was a touch plain at the latest effort but the two wins prior to start the campaign were full of merit. Worth another chance. PARETO (1) grows a leg for hoop Peisley who has two wins from as many steers. May earn some minor money.
